Speedbreaker pulls up beside Dead-End and Drag Strip. "Well if theyre 
ready or not we sure are gonna. I swear, Maximals are even sissier 
than Autobots, I could swear that Firearm was looking at me funny 
before we blew his tail-pipe up!" He said furiously.

Motormaster drove on, listening to the conversation, but not paying 
to much attention. He didnt care for all the talk, but as long as it 
got them motivated.
